data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!! This gorgeous 4 bed 2.5 bath home is in pristine condition! Found on a large lot in delightful South Haven Subdivision, this property is in flood zone x and did not flood in 2016. Walk through the lovely foyer area into the spacious living room. Next, you will enjoy a breakfast nook, granite counter tops, stainless appliances, lots of cabinetry with a walk-in pantry located in a large kitchen leading back to a formal dining room. The Master bedroom has a huge walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom featuring double vanities, a soaking tub, a separate shower and a water closet. There is also a half bathroom on the 1st level for guests. Upstairs there is a sizable landing that can be used as another living area, game room, study area and more. There are also 3 additional bedrooms and another full bathroom. Sitting in a great community boasting of lakes and an outstanding school district, this home is perfect for raising a family or retirement.
